--------Problem 1-----------------
Run the container Hello World:
"docker container run -it hello-world"

Check the Container status:
- i ran using -a becuase the container exited after creation
"docker container ps -a"

Start the stopped container:
"docker container start -i c310"

Delete container and image:
"docker container rm c310"
"docker rmi hello-world"


-------Problem 2--------------------
Run Container centos in interactive mode:
"docker container run -it centos:centos7"

Run echo docker:
"echo docker"

create text file:
"touch hello-world"

stop the container the remove it:
"docker container stop d314"
"docker container rm d314"

remove all stopped containers:
"docker container prune -f"



----------Problem 3-----------------
run container httpd and attach volume
"docker container run -it -v /home/ali/vol1:/usr/local/apache2/htdocs/ -p 9000:80 httpd"

remove container:
"docker container rm e314"

run a new container:
"docker container run -it -v /home/ali/vol1:/usr/local/apache2/htdocs/ -p 9000:80 httpd"



-------Problem 4--------------------
run the image again:
"docker container run -it httpd"

add html static file:
"cp staticWebPage.html /var/lib/docker/overlay2/9c2876c1cfeabcfef035f5115fa4c0d741516f6aa5d6b96b83bab60c0ae913ea/diff/ali"

- first i made a directory called ali to appear in the diff folder of the container
- then i copied the static html file to the diff/ali

commit the container:
"docker commit 29a9 httpd_ali"

Create Dockerfile:

FROM httpd_ali

WORKDIR /ali

RUN mv staticWebPage.html /usr/local/apache2/htdocs/

WORKDIR /usr/local/apache2/htdocs/

RUN rm index.html && mv staticWebPage.html index.html

EXPOSE 80


-----Problem 5-----------
Create a volume:
"docker volume create mysql_data"

Deploy volume:
"docker container run -it -v mysql_data:/var/lib/mysql -e MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD=P4sSw0rd0! mysql:latest"
